text: HAT-P-11b is an extrasolar planet. It is also called Kepler-3b. It orbits the star HAT-P-11. It was discovered by the HATNet Project team in 2009 using the transit method. == Characteristics == It orbits about 0.0534 AU (7,990,000 km) away from its star. It is a hot Neptunes. == References == Category:Exoplanets
title: HAT-P-11b
